{
  "stem": "11552.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know how he got home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I never heard the whole story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the time when they came for him, it was a terrible night, of course.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The NKVD, as we know them now as the KGB, any criminal acts they committed, or arrested was always the middle of the night to frighten people and to bring them into shock.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But my father followed my brother and went with him to Chortkiv, and pleaded with them to let them go.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He didn't say anything, not a word.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But they didn't trust him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So he had to pay with his life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "As I mentioned before, he was a very good chess player.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In prison, he made chess figurines out of bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so the commander of the prison send us a letter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In these figurines, he said my brother lived, he would have been a chess champion.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They let us know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The prison commander wrote to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they wouldn't let us bring him home for burial.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had to be buried there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's ironic.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I was later under the German occupation imprisoned in the same prison and thrown to be buried at the same cemetery when they beat me to death.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was thinking at the time that my brother Moshe is buried here someplace.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's interesting.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it seemed like the light went out of there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father had so much beauty, so much light, and so much joy in his eyes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so did my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But some kind of, like a film, came over their eyes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was laughter then but not quite the way it used to be before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I imagined, and I understood that losing a child was the most horrible thing in a parent's life.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
